Conversely, if $\eta$ : R $\rightarrow$ G is a Lie group homomorphism, then X = d$\eta$( dt ) satisﬁes
\end{flushleft}


\begin{flushleft}
$\eta$ = $\xi$X . Hence, the correspondence X $\rightarrow$ $\xi$X establishes a bijection between g and the
