\end{flushleft}


\begin{flushleft}
whereas the ones appearing in the right-hand side are both in L2 (Rd ), in the time
\end{flushleft}


\begin{flushleft}
domain or in the frequency domain, as one prefers, because of Parseval's equality.
\end{flushleft}


\begin{flushleft}
